auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg" width="706" height="615.7888888888889" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:785,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:706,&quot;bytes&quot;:176711,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3373518-4a44-4e83-b210-e0f092dd391e_900x785.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://x.com/Mark_J_Perry/status/1747995005518516419">马克·佩里</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这里的基础数据没有问题——它来自劳工统计局。美国劳工统计局并不总是让一切都完美无缺——没有人做到这一点——但他们竭尽全力，而且他们有很多聪明的人不知疲倦地工作，以使这些数据尽可能准确。</p><p>我对该图表呈现数据的方式确实有两个小问题。首先，大学学费数字是<em>标题</em>数字，不包括<em>经济援助</em>。学生实际支付的大学学费<a href="https://libertystreeteconomics.newyorkfed.org/2019/06/the-cost-of-college-continues-to-climb/">增长速度比官方标价慢得多</a>，并且<a href="https://www.brookings.edu/articles/college-prices-arent-skyrocketing-but-theyre-still-too-high-for-some/">在2006年之后根本没有增长</a>。其次，佩里选择将住房和食品标记为红色，因为它们的上涨速度略快于总体通货膨胀率，这一点有点可疑——两者的增长速度都比工资慢，因此在这段时间内它们变得<em>更加负担得起</em>，而不是更少。 。</p><p>但这些都是小问题。总体而言，这是一张具有良好数据的良好图表，它说明了近几十年来美国经济的一个清晰而重要的事实：<strong>实物商品普遍变得更便宜，而服务普遍变得更昂贵</strong>。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://x.com/search?q=%22chart%20of%20the%20century%22%20government&amp;src=typed_query&amp;f=top">许多人看到这张图表</a>后，相信它揭示了服务价格上涨的<em>根本原因</em>。他们认为这完全取决于政府的参与和监管： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg" width="612" height="258.4595185995624" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2e2eac1a-49b6-4783-ba85-c3f42c8dacc3_914x386.jpeg&qu