Decade of the BatteryA repost with some updates. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/decade-of-the-battery-334 https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/decade-of-the-battery-334Noah Smith Sun, 09 Jun 2024 06:59:56 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg" width="1183" height="790" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:790,&quot;width&quot;:1183,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:33845,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fae0f0dbd-6aa7-4197-99bd-cc89f5c4f27f_1183x790.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">照片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@asoggetti?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Alessio Soggetti</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/turned-on-drone-rSFxBGpnluw?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄</figcaption></figure></div><p><em>2022 年，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/decade-of-the-battery">我写了一篇文章</a>，认为电池将成为 2020 年代的决定性技术。距离 ChatGPT 发布和生成式人工智能蓬勃发展仅几个月。鉴于这种突然的盛行，不起眼的电池可能看起来古朴而平淡，而我的帖子可能看起来可笑地不合时宜。</em></p><p><em>然而两年后，我认为我的职位仍然有效。这两年见证了小型电池驱动无人机彻底改变了<a href="https://www.technologyreview.com/2023/01/30/1067348/mass-market-military-drones-have-changed-the-way-wars-are-fought/">战争的方式</a>。他们已经看到，电池存储成为太阳能的普遍补充，<a href="https://x.com/drvolts/status/1793743067645972773">解决了太阳能的几乎所有</a>间歇性问题，并在全球范围内吸引了大量的投资。电池为<a href="https://www.technologyreview.com/2023/02/21/1068880/how-did-china-dominate-electric-cars-policy/">中国汽车行业</a>的突然迅速崛起提供了动力，该汽车行业从同时的运输工具转变为突然有可能占据整个全球汽车市场的王室。人工智能当然是神奇的，具有令人难以置信的潜力，但是在短短几年内，电池开始改变人类的能源供应，战争，运输和地缘政治优势。</em></p><p><em>同样，很快就会显然，在许多方面，AI和电池都是完美的补充技术。无人机现在是人类的，但是<a href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/drone-swarms-are-about-to-change-the-balance-of-military-power-e091aa6f">自主的无人机群</a>即将到来，他们将再次改变战争和权力平衡。 AI承诺将机器人技术从利基类型的机床转换为<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/techno-optimism-for-2024">我们世界上无处不在的特征</a>。自主机的兴起将是 - 必须是 - 电池供电。</em></p><p><em>因此，这是我从2022年开始的帖子。看看您认为它仍然有多坚持。</em></p><div><hr></div><p> 2015年，本尼迪克特·埃文斯（Benedict Evans）撰写了一篇非常有影响力的文章，名为“<a href="https://twitter.com/benedictevans/status/627884650300506113">智能手机是新的太阳</a>”。到2010年代中期，很明显，史蒂夫·乔布斯（Steve Jobs）在2007年揭幕的移动计算平台将以许多方式定义那十年。将它们连接到数字世界，并允许他们浏览物理世界。对于行业而言，智能手机及其启用的应用已成为投资和利润的巨大机会。</p><p>但是，现在，似乎我们可能正在到达那个彩虹的尽头。基本原因是，使用智能手机，IT公司现在已经收获了所有人们的剩余关注和时间。 <a href="https://www.pewresearch.org/internet/2022/08/10/teens-social-media-and-technology-2022/">对青少年社交媒体习惯的一项新的皮尤调查</a>发现，几乎一半的年轻人几乎在网上几乎不断地”，高于2010年代中期的四分之一。富裕国家的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_countries_by_smartphone_penetration">智能手机渗透率</a>约为80％。因此，对于消费者和投资者/企业家来说，寻找技术可以在未来十年中引起寒武纪创新的另一个技术爆炸是很自然的。</p><p>许多人认为这项技术将是机器学习/AI。但是，尽管我确实认为ML确实非常重要，但我将提出一个论点，即真正改变我们社会的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/General-purpose_technology">通用技术</a>是电池。</p><p>这很有趣，因为这与过去四十年的模式有点转弯。从1980  -  2020年开始，重塑我们世界的创新都在信息技术中 -  PC，Internet，智能手机和社交网络。但是电池是一种“原子”技术，它可以为我们的物理世界提供动力，而不是帮助我们旋转新的数字技术。因此，电池的十年看起来更像是早些几十年，在这些电池中，洗衣机，冰箱和空调等物理设备<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/technology-adoption">是热门的新事物</a>。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png" width="1456" height="1028" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1028,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:992889,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7dc6442b-7b87-4254-b943-5d9e1d963de3_3400x2400.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>实际上，我们已经可以看到2010年代的转变 - 毕竟，电池是启用智能手机的原因。</p><p>电池变得如此重要的基本原因仅仅是该技术通过飞跃和界限改进。尽管<a href="https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlehtml/2021/ee/d0ee02681f">电池实际上正在改善任何度量</a>，但两个最清晰的指标是成本和能量密度。自1991年以来，电池成本以每千瓦时的库存为美元，自2010年以来下降了42倍，次数为2.5倍： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png" width="1363" height="1267" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d6000456-d2d8-479b-92f9-16684ffba756_1363x1267.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;h