ge/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png" width="561" height="523" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/aa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:523,&quot;width&quot;:561,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:208442,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Faa5e5cfc-598d-4947-8ceb-192ad1dec7e9_561x523.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlehtml/2021/ee/d0ee02681f">Ziegler＆Trancik（2021）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这一改进的狮子份额<a href="https://news.mit.edu/2021/lithium-ion-battery-cost-1122">归因于研发的努力</a>，但工业规模的影响也开始产生重大影响。</p><p>但是，当然，这仍然留下了将要<em>使用</em>哪些电池的基本问题。从明显的（汽车和能源）到不太明显的用例，我将经历一堆用例。但是首先，我应该谈谈<em>为什么</em>电池是这样的通用技术。</p><h4>电池一次解决两个基本问题</h4><p>能源显然对每个工业社会都是至关重要的，它对于物理（“原子”）技术（例如运输，制造，电力和电器）尤其重要。我们经常从<em>主要</em>能源来思考 - 也就是说，我们从哪里获得能量。太阳能和风能，核和水力发电等技术也提供了这种需求，当然，燃烧化石燃料也可以做到这一点。电池不这样做。</p><p>但是，能量不仅仅是产生。我们还必须<em>存储</em>能量，我们必须从一个地方<em>运输</em>它。换句话说，我们必须在时间和空间中移动能量，以便我们可以随时随地使用它。电池解决这两个问题。</p><p>在存储方面，电池还不如化石燃料，因为它们会随着时间的流逝而泄漏能量。这就是为什么它们可以用于发电厂和网格的短期储能，但不能用于季节性存储。但是，对于运输能源，电池在质量上比化石燃料优越。首先，基本上可以通过任何电源来充电电池，而石油管道或天然气箱只能真正容纳一种特定类型的化石燃料。其次，从电池中提取能量通常要比使用燃烧引擎提取能量要嘈杂得多。还有其他优势。</p><p>不过，最重要的是，电池不需要笨重的燃烧引擎才能提取能量。当我在2020年夏天读到波特兰抗议者时，我首先意识到了这一点的重要性<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEqRIkVEya0">，该抗议者使用电池驱动的叶轮在联邦代理商面前吹催泪瓦斯</a>。电池驱动的叶轮比汽油驱动的叶子强大，但<a href="https://www.gardentoolexpert.com/electric-vs-gas-leaf-blowers-what-do-you-choose/">它们也轻得多</a>。这就是为什么我们将电池用于小型轻量级无人机的原因。这是您的智能手机中有电池而不是汽油供电的发动机的重要部分。</p><p>每当电池怀疑论者告诉您，电池的能量密度低于化石燃料，请将其指向它们。</p><p>随着电池的不断改善，与化石燃料相比，它们的缺点将减少。我们将开发具有更长寿命，更大功率密度等的电池。</p><h4>明显的用例 - 汽车和电源存储</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F70980ee9-2611-40e4-a56d-530570a8bbe9_1024x766.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-951