"retweets"><span class="rt-count">4个</span>转发</span></div></div></div><p>尽管公用事业的存储是一个小得多的市场，但也正在迅速增加： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png" width="923" height="469" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:469,&quot;width&quot;:923,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:89716,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F12ad31ea-4bb8-402a-8621-ae4bc0bcafa1_923x469.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>公用事业规模或建筑规模的储能不会真正改变我们的日常生活，实际上，一般的想法是<em>防止</em>我们的日常生活在我们用可再生能源替换化石燃料时不得不改变。但是，电动汽车肯定会使世界的感觉与众不同。</p><p>首先，由于电动汽车在晚上充电，这意味着您只需要填满您的汽车，而不必每次储罐空的时都去加油站。随着电动汽车的射程更好 -<a href="https://www.gearpatrol.com/cars/g40365538/longest-range-electric-car/">现在它们非常接近汽油汽车</a>- 这将意味着人们<em>几乎永远不必</em>停下来填充，因为他们的汽车总是会在早上开始充满电。一个大的时间浪费 - 正在寻找加油站，坐在罐子里时坐在有毒的烟雾周围 - 大部分都会消失。一旦我们得到这些，自动驾驶汽车的自动付费也比抽动自己的汽油要容易得多。</p><p>其次，电动汽车比汽油汽车安静得多 - 如此安静，以至于<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/7/1/20676854/electric-cars-artificial-safety-noise-low-speeds-european-union-rules-2019-2021">我们实际上必须</a><em><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2019/7/1/20676854/electric-cars-artificial-safety-noise-low-speeds-european-union-rules-2019-2021">添加噪音</a></em>，以防止孩子们在街上奔跑！ <a href="https://hmmh.com/resources/news-insights/blog/will-electric-cars-result-in-quieter-communities/">电动卡车将使居住在高速公路附近</a>，大型通道少得多。</p><p>最后，电动汽车只是使驾驶更好的体验。它们的<a href="https://www.greencarreports.com/news/1075727_electric-cars-secret-advantage-theyre-just-nicer-to-drive">响应速度比汽油汽车更快</a>，而且填充也便宜得多。想要改用以公交为中心的发展的人<a href="https://noahpinion.substack.com/p/we-will-not-ban-cars">不会喜欢这样</a>，但是没有骑火车的人会很高兴。</p><p>因此，众所周知的电池用例已经变得非常大。但是，此外，还有很多不太明显但仍然具有变换性的电池依赖性技术，这些技术也正在迅速增长。</p><h4>不要睡在电动自行车上</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bbb99b8-254a-4da1-afc9-a3576fe429ea_1024x683.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3bbb99b8-254a-4da1-afc9-a3576fe429ea_1024x683.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimag