ge/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png" width="788" height="474" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:474,&quot;width&quot;:788,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:20022,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc6d3986b-381a-4cb7-8ebe-20f6ea17edf2_788x474.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p> E-Bikes <a href="https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2022/01/19/2369598/0/en/Global-Electric-Bike-Market-Share-Poised-to-Reflect-14-9-CAGR-by-2028-to-Hit-USD-69-24-Billion-Eco-Friendly-Mobility-is-Boosting-e-Bikes-Demand-Says-Facts-Factors.html">在全球范围内已经是一家耗资400亿美元的业务</a>，并且迅速增长。</p><p>电子自行车不像普通自行车 - 它们为您的肌肉力量增添了电力，从而使行驶更加容易。这以两种方式改变了骑自行车。首先，它可以让您走得更远。 <a href="https://www.treehugger.com/e-bikers-ride-much-farther-and-more-frequently-than-regula-bikers-5076231">从最近在挪威的一项研究</a>中：</p><blockquote><blockquote><p>购买电子自行车的人将自行车使用从2.1公里（1.3英里）增加到平均每天的9.2公里（5.7英里）；增加了340％。 E-Bike在所有运输中的份额也大大增加了。从17％到49％，他们骑自行车而不是走路，进行公共交通和开车……。事实上，人们拥有他们的电子自行车越长，他们骑了他们的自行车[。]。</p></blockquote></blockquote><p>其次，电子自行车使<a href="https://cyclebaron.com/how-good-are-electric-bikes-going-uphill/">骑自行车非常容易上坡</a>。这为骑自行车的人打开了巨大的区域，这些区域基本上是在基本上被拒绝的（例如，旧金山的大部分地区）。</p><p>更长的范围和不必担心道路等级的组合意味着电子摩托车有可能改变我们的生活方式。由于美国已经有道路，可以在尚不存在的自行车道上增加自行车道，因此转换城市以容纳大量电子自行车通勤者的成本不会很大（当然要比建造火车要小！）。而且，由于电动自行车较小且易于停车，因此我们可以在靠近共同目的地的附近建造许多自行车架，从而消除了通勤时找到停车位的一些麻烦。</p><p>总而言之，电子自行车只会使绕过我们的城市变得更加容易，这希望会增加人类的联系并使我们感到更加自由。它们还将使许多领域的食物和产品交付变得更加容易。而且，由于电子自行车仍然使用一点肌肉力量，我们也可能会变得更健康！</p><p>还值得注意的是，电动<a href="https://www.fastcompany.com/90738126/this-startup-designed-an-electric-cargo-ship-to-cross-the-ocean">货船</a>和<a href="https://www.afar.com/magazine/electric-planes-are-coming-sooner-than-you-think">飞机</a>正在管道中，尽管我不希望这些船在未来十年内会变得普遍。</p><h4>无人机是战争的未来</h4><p>电池不仅会改变平民运输，而且还将改变军用车辆，从而实现全新的战争方式。任何关注乌克兰战争的人都已经知道这一点。尽管像Bayraktar这样的燃烧动力无人机引起了大部分关注，但Little Electric Drones已经开始在战场上相对接近的范围内进行精确罢工。这是一个视频： </p><div data-component-name="Twitter2ToDOM" class="tweet" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/kirbygriffin17/status/1561980980440616960&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Ukrainian Drone Drops Grenade directly into a Russian Tank with crew sti... <a class=\&quot;tweet-url\&quot; href=\&quot;https://youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lpocd4?feature=share\&quot;>youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lp&#8230;</a> via <span class=\&quot;tweet-fake-link\&quot;>@YouTube</span>&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;kirbygriffin17&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;kirby griffin&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Tue Aug 23 07:37:40 +0000 2022&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:1,&quot;like_count&quot;:1,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://youtube.com/shorts/I-XK_lpocd4?feature=share&quot;,&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://bucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3b0ec7cd-52a1-4119-942e-aa5129c10594_480x360.jpeg&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Ukrainian Drone Drops Grenade directly into