仅是因为乌克兰的钱较少，而且被迫诉诸便宜的糟糕武器。<a href="https://twitter.com/RALee85/status/1560404144132964355">俄罗斯人也在使用电池供电的无人机</a>。当然，这些无人机对于战场侦察也<a href="https://www.stimson.org/2022/drone-warfare-in-ukraine-understanding-the-landscape/">非常有用</a>，这对于针对现代精密武器至关重要。</p><p>廉价可靠的能量密度电池的出现使这成为可能。电池供电的无人机很小，便宜且相对安静。在增加地缘政治竞争和冲突的时代，军事无人机的创新可能才刚刚开始。反人选的无人机将士兵从密集的城市地区清除，对周围建筑物的损害最小。也开发了<a href="https://www.extremetech.com/extreme/335095-scientists-develop-swarm-of-inescapable-autonomous-drones">自动群的无人机</a>。电池供电的机器人可能<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2021/4/7/22371590/boston-dynamics-spot-robot-military-exercises-french-army">有助于将设备运送到战场上</a>，甚至可以携带和射击以前保留给步兵的武器。</p><p>在极端情况下，人类可以完全从战场上驱逐。其尺寸小，重量轻，价格便宜的电池可能对此至关重要。</p><h4>电池供电</h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdd58c1ed-df36-43f8-8b48-029b91be5af9_3000x2250.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2F